``


Parameters
spark (required)
Active SparkSession.
Used for:

schema validation
DataFrame creation
writing to Delta


collection_instance_id (optional)
Default collection instance identifier for this logger.
Use this when:

all events in the task relate to the same collection instance

In DataFrame logging, this can be overridden per row using:

collection_instance_id_column

If omitted, the value may be NULL unless overridden.

task_key (optional)
Task key for the current workflow step.
If omitted:

Databricks Job task_key is used when available
otherwise defaults to "unknown"

Useful when:

